"programmes futurs et [...] passés dans le domaine public.&nbsp;» Consultez "
"<url id=\"http://cr.yp.to/distributors.html\" name=\"la FAQ des distributeurs"
"\"> pour les termes de sa distribution."

#. type: <p></p>
#: debian-faq.sgml:46 software.sgml:200
msgid ""
"As of 2008-09, <package>daemontools</package>, <package>djbdns</package> and "
"<package>ucspi-tcp</package> are shipped with Debian lenny (in main). As of "
