"org/457318\" name=\"Bug #457318 (ITP qmail)\"> and <url id=\"http://bugs."
"debian.org/469193\" name=\"Bug #469193 (ITP ezmlm-idx)\"> for the current "
"status."
msgstr ""
"Depuis septembre 2008, <package>daemontools</package>, <package>djbdns</"
